adept.common

Class DocumentRelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.Item
      • adept.common.HltContent
        • adept.common.DocumentRelation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasScoredUnaryAttributes

    public final class DocumentRelation
extends HltContent
implements HasScoredUnaryAttributes

    Represents a relation at the level of participating document-level entities, rather than strings of text. The arguments of this class must necessarily be references to document-level entities or temporal values, i.e. instances of class Entity or TemporalValue. In future releases, arguments will also be allowed to reference a numerical value.

    Objects of this class are associated with provenances that are instances of RelationMention.

    This is a new class introduced in the API release version 2.0, and is the primary class to be used in inserting relations into the Adept KB.
